  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Combine the <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>soy sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the juice of 1/2<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>brown sugar </strong>in a bowl and mix to combine<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> lime & peanut marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1613745144884-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1613745144884-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1613745144884-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1613745144884-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1613745144884-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chicken breast strips</strong> to the <strong>lime & peanut marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>peanut butter chicken</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>peanut butter chicken</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!) and drizzle any <strong>remaining marinade</strong> over the chicken</p><p>Put the tray under the grill for 10 min, turning once, or until the chicken is cooked through and beginning to char (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1613745180059-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1613745180059-x400.jpg",
