    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped peppers</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
