    {
      "instruction": "<p>Take the pan off the heat and add in the juice of the <strong>remaining lime </strong>and the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong></p><p>Mix everything together so the noodles are fully coated in the sauce – these are your <strong>vibrant noodles</strong></p>",
